## 🎯 Pattern Recognition Guide

| 🔍 Problem Type  | 💡 Trick                   |
| ---------------- | -------------------------- |
| Count subarrays  | Use **frequency map**      |
| Longest subarray | Store **first occurrence** |
| Equal 0s & 1s    | Convert `0 → -1`           |
| Divisible by K   | Use **modulo logic**       |

